---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions — TED Talk Finder | AI-Powered TED Talk Discovery"
  description="Review the Terms and Conditions of TED Talk Finder. Learn about service usage rules, disclaimer of affiliation with TED Conferences LLC, and API policies."
  canonicalUrl="https://tedtalksfinder.com/terms-and-conditions"
>
  <!-- Nav -->
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-black text-white py-16 sm:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p
        class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#EB0028] mb-4"
      >
        Legal Terms
      </p>
      <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight leading-none mb-6"
      >
        Terms &amp;<br /><span class="text-[#EB0028]">Conditions</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Please read these Terms and Conditions carefully before using the TED
        Talk Finder website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="bg-white py-12 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
      <section
        class="prose max-w-none text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6"
      >
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            1. Agreement to Terms
          </h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using TED Talk Finder, you agree to be bound by
            these Terms and Conditions, all applicable laws and regulations, and
            agree that you are responsible for compliance with any applicable
            local laws. If you do not agree with any of these terms, you are
            prohibited from using or accessing this site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            2. Affiliation Disclaimer
          </h2>
          <p class="font-semibold text-black">
            TED Talk Finder is an independent, fan-made curation and discovery
            tool. We are not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or
            in any way officially connected with TED Conferences LLC, or any of
            its subsidiaries or its affiliates.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            The official TED website can be found at <a
              href="https://www.ted.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-[#EB0028] hover:underline">https://www.ted.com</a
            >. The name "TED" as well as related names, marks, emblems, and
            images are registered trademarks of their respective owners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            3. Intellectual Property Rights &amp; YouTube
          </h2>
          <p>
            This application uses YouTube API Services to retrieve public video
            metadata from the official TED channel. All video content, titles,
            trademarks, and associated copyright materials remain the property
            of TED Conferences LLC and the respective speakers.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            By using this application to discover and watch video cards linked
            to YouTube, you acknowledge and agree that your actions are also
            governed by the YouTube Terms of Service (<a
              href="https://www.youtube.com/t/terms"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-[#EB0028] hover:underline"
              >https://www.youtube.com/t/terms</a
            >).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            4. Use License &amp; Restrictions
          </h2>
          <p>
            You are granted a temporary, non-exclusive, non-transferable license
            to access the search utility for personal, non-commercial
            educational purposes. Under this license, you may not:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Modify or copy any code or stylesheet frameworks.</li>
            <li>
              Use the search endpoints or backend services for scraping or
              automated data retrieval.
            </li>
            <li>
              Attempt to bypass rate limits or interfere with the service's API
              rotation keys.
            </li>
            <li>
              Remove any copyright or proprietary notations from the materials.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            5. Disclaimer of Warranties
          </h2>
          <p>
            The materials on TED Talk Finder are provided on an 'as is' basis.
            We make no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaim and
            negate all other warranties including, without limitation, implied
            warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a
            particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property or
            other violation of rights.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Further, we do not warrant or make any representations concerning
            the accuracy, likely results, or reliability of the use of the
            materials on our website or otherwise relating to such materials or
            on any sites linked to this site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            6. Limitations of Liability
          </h2>
          <p>
            In no event shall TED Talk Finder or its developers be liable for
            any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data
            or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use
            or inability to use the materials on TED Talk Finder, even if an
            authorized representative has been notified orally or in writing of
            the possibility of such damage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-3 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2"
          >
            7. Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p>
            Any claim relating to TED Talk Finder shall be governed by the laws
            of our operating jurisdiction, without regard to its conflict of law
            provisions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="bg-black text-white p-8 sm:p-12 text-center mt-12">
        <p
          class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#EB0028] mb-4"
        >
          Start Discovering
        </p>
        <h2
          class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight mb-4"
        >
          Explore Verified TED Talks
        </h2>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block bg-[#EB0028] text-white font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs sm:text-sm px-8 py-4 hover:bg-[#c40020] transition-colors duration-150"
        >
          Find Talks Now
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer
    class="bg-black text-white py-10 px-4 sm:py-12 sm:px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-gray-900"
  >
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-gray-600 gap-4 text-center sm:text-left"
    >
      <div>
        &copy; 2026 TED Talk Finder. Built with Astro &amp; Tailwind CSS v4.
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"
          >Privacy Policy</a
        >
        <a
          href="/terms-and-conditions"
          class="hover:text-white transition-colors text-white">Terms</a
        >
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
